{"tid":550973,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"去過法國交流請入指教","createTime":"2018-02-05T08:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T01:47:11.000Z","uid":138331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf2aa7717ea194c634f878b0583cbb798f75e64","tid":550973,"uid":138331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打C打去過法蘭西交流<br />\n有咩感覺或者建議？<br />\n或者會唔會有咩特別感受？<br />\n如果我半句法文唔識，<br />\n會唔會好大困難？<br />\n<br />\n派左去土魯斯，法國南部，地中海傍，西班牙隔離。<br />\n<br />\n緊急，禮拜五要決定去唔去。<br />\n有冇巴絲可以幫下手。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377bcc3456889dd77277fa354146e6bd72ccacbc","tid":550973,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"583f427e9ce65d67e50497ae83fde6f96981814b","tid":550973,"uid":42992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"Tbs?"},{"pid":"8897c3e73c1daf805e73e710511637d42c8f2774","tid":550973,"uid":80329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"法國搞簽證好鬼煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出到去會覺得香港太井底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有機會去exchange緊喺去啦<br />\n仲可以歐遊添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 喺法國讀緊social science 俾人屌打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bd8aa2a4737279872ce86be2d4e921b6341509","tid":550973,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8897c3e73c1daf805e73e710511637d42c8f2774","tid":550973,"uid":80329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"法國搞簽證好鬼煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出到去會覺得香港太井底<img