ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2b68a6ae4c453789eb32f23331750a00ed767e","tid":550973,"uid":86487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T21:48:44.000Z","msg":"我去果陣都唔識法文,但我去巴黎D人基本上都識講英文,只要你用法文開頭問野,之後轉番CHANNEL用番英文就OK<br />\n<br />\n你一開波就用英文D撚樣會西你臉扮聽唔明。"},{"pid":"0bb5f9350700d8f800c3ccd9c5bd7895b492e9a1","tid":550973,"uid":85821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T22:40:07.000Z","msg":"唔識法文真係有啲難搞 啲法國人好鬼寸 其實基本上生活上所有野都要用法文溝通 好少人識英文<br />\n前年去exchange 宿舍嗰條receptionist用英文同我講佢唔識聽英文 淨係可以講法文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 而家fulltime喺里昂讀緊"},{"pid":"965066eb754baaecb5b940dbd995601505c88721","tid":550973,"uid":80329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:00:25.000Z","msg":"原來有咁多位爸打絲打留法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲以為自己喺異類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n法國最恐怖其實喺佢個 la dissertation 格式<br />\n寫essay要重新學過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲長麵包又喺<br />\n真喺狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3ad0ba9022b5ec245e648f7cff8c75f98b67e2","tid":550973,"uid":80329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:03:08.000Z","msg":"不過去留學特別喺法國依個一開始語言不通嘅環境真喺會令到人成熟咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92602741714273d9e81e8a2a4817e9dbe2ae5adc","tid":550973,"uid":85821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:04:02.000Z","msg":"同埋去完你會發現香港人做嘢真係好有效率"},{"pid":"9ed284d6189222c3dc0cb23ae2f17ae784175301","tid":550973,"uid":22074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:14:24.000Z","msg":"仲有法國仔真係好撚臭，陣味好似10日無沖涼再勁噴香水咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34c9167e6fece5ee0b4a3f5413cea3d54b34419","tid":550973,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T01:11:56.000Z","msg":"最好要識少少法文<br />\n唔係會有好多溝通障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cab6b8318b63fb4acc4f64ac56ed2f5d402364b","tid":550973,"uid":60617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T01:18:41.000Z","msg":"我就唔係交流<br />\n十年前去咗波爾多附近小鎮讀兩年<br />\n一去到都係唔識法文<br />\n好彩有唔少同學同老師都肯教<br />\n我自己覺得學法文係三個月為一個階段，最緊要係你肯講肯學多聽<br />\nToulouse 好呀 東行南法意大利 西行就西班牙<br />\n<br />\n出去見識下 一定有得著！"},{"pid":"05a30df59fc7f6736164e5ed2d0410240dc1aaa9","tid":550973,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7fecb3775ef78bd0bd805cad0892cbc04652ed6","tid":550973,"uid":80329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77bd8aa2a4737279872ce86be2d4e921b6341509","tid":550973,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8897c3e73c1daf805e73e710511637d42c8f2774","tid":550973,"uid":80329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"法國搞簽證好鬼煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出到去會覺得香港太井底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有機會去exchange緊喺去啦<br />\n仲可以歐遊添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 喺法國讀緊social science 俾人屌打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T18:07:13.000Z","msg":"Sciences Po?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T18:11:15.000Z","msg":"出黎乞硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T01:22:04.000Z","msg":"你係咪跟hku個joint degree programme入sciences po？"},{"pid":"9cea8564487b1f779deb936ea5a3234886474ba5","tid":550973,"uid":80329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05a30df59fc7f6736164e5ed2d0410240dc1aaa9","tid":550973,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7fecb3775ef78bd0bd805cad0892cbc04652